40:53.451 --> 40:56.321
(melancholy music)

41:07.966 --> 41:10.602
- Hey, hey, I'm here.

41:10.602 --> 41:12.838
It's okay, I'm not
going anywhere.

41:17.643 --> 41:19.978
I don't think this
is the time to-

41:19.978 --> 41:21.479
- Just agree, I want to.

41:21.479 --> 41:22.313
- Liz-

41:22.313 --> 41:23.314
- No Roberta,

41:24.149 --> 41:25.450
