42:58.043 --> 42:59.678
- What's too important?

42:59.678 --> 43:01.780
- You cutting this bitch loose.

43:04.082 --> 43:06.752
- No, I am not
taking this from you.

43:08.887 --> 43:11.389
(tense music)

43:31.542 --> 43:32.878
