43:48.459 --> 43:49.294
- Who?

43:52.297 --> 43:53.464
- Payton and Seth.

43:55.734 --> 43:56.567
- They were here?

44:02.640 --> 44:03.775
Well, they're gone now.

44:05.643 --> 44:06.477
I'm here.

44:09.314 --> 44:10.415
They're gone.

44:17.455 --> 44:22.460
