1:21:06.495 --> 1:21:08.231
(Liz sighs)

1:21:08.231 --> 1:21:11.234
Brody, you scared me.

1:21:11.234 --> 1:21:13.903
(clock chiming)

1:21:23.012 --> 1:21:25.681
Okay Brody, time for
a meditation break.

1:21:27.016 --> 1:21:27.850
Join me?

1:21:29.885 --> 1:21:32.388
Okay, fine, you do you.

1:21:33.722 --> 1:21:36.425
(doorbell rings)

1:21:37.393 --> 1:21:38.394
Who is it?

1:21:38.427 --> 1:21:39.528
- [Pizza Man] Pizza man.

1:21:39.562 --> 1:21:40.496
- Pizza?

1:21:40.496 --> 1:21:42.498
I didn't order any pizza.

1:21:42.531 --> 1:21:43.866
- [Pizza Man] It says
your name, ma'am.

1:21:43.866 --> 1:21:44.833
- What's the name?

1:21:46.602 --> 1:21:48.204
I said what's the name?

1:21:50.339 --> 1:21:52.241
- [Pizza Man] It says
this address ma'am.

1:21:52.241 --> 1:21:53.409
- [Liz] What's the name?

1:21:54.710 --> 1:21:56.045
- [Pizza Man] Excuse me?

1:21:56.079 --> 1:21:58.247
- What's the name on the order?

1:21:58.247 --> 1:21:59.515
- [Pizza Man] Having a
hard time hearing you.

1:21:59.515 --> 1:22:02.685
It's one pizza,
extra ham, ma'am.

1:22:02.685 --> 1:22:04.053
- Okay, but what's the name?

1:22:09.358 --> 1:22:11.027
I think you have
the wrong house.

1:22:12.261 --> 1:22:13.462
- [Pizza Man] Ma'am?

1:22:13.529 --> 1:22:15.931
- Oh my God, I said you
have the wrong house!

1:22:15.931 --> 1:22:18.901
(dramatic music)

1:22:18.934 --> 1:22:21.437
(Payton growls)

1:22:21.437 --> 1:22:24.273
(machine beeping)

1:22:28.311 --> 1:22:30.479
- I think we've done
all we can do here.

1:22:30.479 --> 1:22:31.580
Call it.

1:22:31.614 --> 1:22:34.283
- Time of death, 11:52 PM.

1:22:34.283 --> 1:22:37.486
Cause of death, blood
loss due to shark bite.

1:22:37.553 --> 1:22:39.488
- Nurse Quan, make
any arrangements.

1:22:39.488 --> 1:22:40.489
- [Quan] Yes Doctor.

1:22:42.558 --> 1:22:44.393
- She put up a hell
of a fight though.

1:22:44.393 --> 1:22:45.761
- Yeah, she sure did.

1:22:50.466 --> 1:22:53.136
(Roberta sighs)

1:22:58.974 --> 1:23:01.844
(slow gentle music)

1:23:13.522 --> 1:23:17.693
* My love

1:23:17.693 --> 1:23:21.430
* Isn't whole

1:23:21.464 --> 1:23:26.469
* With you

1:23:29.205 --> 1:23:34.043
* Sweeping in the sea

1:23:34.043 --> 1:23:39.048
* Where I wanna be

1:23:40.015 --> 1:23:44.453
* You and me

1:23:44.487 --> 1:23:46.655
* My love

1:23:49.325 --> 1:23:52.195
(fast tense music)

1:23:54.397 --> 1:23:57.066
(ominous music)

1:24:00.703 --> 1:24:04.073
(dramatic ominous music)

1:24:36.004 --> 1:24:39.007
(suspenseful music)

1:25:00.363 --> 1:25:02.965
(ominous music)
